<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="ltr" lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8" />
<title>On Device Activation</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
<meta name="description" content="" />
<meta name="keywords" content="" />
<link rel="shortcut icon" href="favicon.ico" />
<style>
div,span,h1,p,a,body {
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0;
	border: 0;
	font-size: 100%;
	vertical-align: baseline;
	font-family: Arial;
}

body {
	background: #ccc;
	font-family: Arial;
}

h1 {
	font-size: 68px;
	font-weight: bold;
	margin-bottom: 20px;
}

p {
	font-size: 16px;
	margin-bottom: 20px;
}

ul {
	margin: 0 0 40px -15px;
}

li {
	margin-bottom: 10px;
}

button {
	background: #E20074;
	border: 1px solid #DADADA;
	border-radius: 5px;
	color: #FFF;
	cursor: pointer;
	font-size: 15px;
	height: 46px;
	margin: 20px 0;
	text-transform: uppercase;
	width: 200px;
}

button:hover {
	background: #ec54a2;
}

.header {
	height: 130px;
}

.header .tmobile-logo {
	float: right;
	width: 250px;
	height: 100px;
	background: url(/upsell/images/connect_me_logo.png)
		no-repeat center center;
	background-size: 250px 82px;
}

.header .tmobile-logo-black {
	display: none;
}

.header .tmobile-logo-pink {
	display: none;
}

html,body,.section_ {
	height: 100%;
}

.content {
	width: 768px;
	background: #E6E7E8;
	margin: 0 auto;
	height: 100%;
}

.content:after {
	background: #e6e7e8;
	content: '';
	display: block;
	height: 100%;
	position: fixed;
}

.section {
	margin: 0 95px;
	padding-top: 20px;
}

@media screen and (max-width: 767px) {
	body {
		background: #E6E7E8;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 54px;
	}
	p {
		font-size: 15px;
	}
	.content {
		width: 100%;
	}
	.section {
		margin: 0 20px;
	}
	.header {
		height: 100px;
	}
	.tmobile-logo-black {
		color: #000000;
		font-size: 1100% !important;
		height: 100px !important;
		left: 30px !important;
	}
	.tmobile-logo-pink {
		font-size: 1100% !important;
		height: 100px !important;
	}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
	<div class="section_">
		<div class="content">
			<div class="section">
				<div class="header">
					<div class="tmobile-logo">
						<div class="tmobile-logo-black icon icon_Logo_black"></div>
						<div class="tmobile-logo-pink icon icon_Logo_pink"></div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<h2>T-Mobile Connect Me</h2>
				<p>Hey, we've been expecting you. You're probably looking to:</p>
				<ul>
					<li>Activate your new device</li>
					<li>Get more data</li>
					<li>Stop reading this and get up n' running</li>
				</ul>
				<p>Ok, let's go!</p>
				<button onClick="location.href='http://mim.t-mobile.com/'">Get Started</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>